# Webshare proxy list
# Format: host:port:username:password (one per line)
#
# Setup:
# 1. Create free account at https://proxy2.webshare.io/register
# 2. Go to Dashboard → Proxy → List
# 3. Click Download → Format: host:port:username:password
# 4. Save downloaded file as data/proxies.txt
#
# Free tier: 10 datacenter proxies, 1GB bandwidth/month
# At ~160 requests/day (~100MB/day), free tier lasts ~10 days/month.
# Consider $2.99/month plan for 250GB if needed.
#
# Example line (not real):
# p.webshare.io:80:abc123xyz:secretpass99
